              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two large NaI detectors (12.7 cm diameter x",
                " 10.2 cm) placed on each side of the target with",
                " crystal to target distance of 1.5 cm. A 0.16 cm",
                " thick lead absorber was placed in front of each NaI",
                " detector to suppress low energy y-rays thickness."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Isotopically enriched (enrichment more than 97 %)",
                " 13C self-supporting foils of 100 and 30 microg/cm2",
                " were used as targets. The thinner target was chosen",
                " to scan, with the laboratory beam energy intervals",
                " of 02 MeV, for resonant fluctuations in the cross",
                " section. At 6.5 < E(lab) < 9.0 MeV only the 100",
                " micorg/cm2 targets gave statistically sufficient",
                " yields"
              ]
            }
